Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.49,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.49,0:00:19.79,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:24.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:37.65,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.65,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:53.40,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.40,0:00:57.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:05.21,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:15.35,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:22.70,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:27.43,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.43,0:01:34.37,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma cherie La Poupee...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma cherie La Poupee...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.34,0:02:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.50,0:02:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.34,0:02:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! She looks just like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma cherie La Poupee.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear, cute little Poupee.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.60,0:03:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}12. The Scar
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Along a ridge in the rolling hills...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...there is a cobblestone road.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A little horse-drawn carriage traverses the path.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.45,0:04:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Koton, koton, kotokoton...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.31,0:04:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...I hear it bumping over the cobblestoned road.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.25,0:04:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...finally it passes over the third hill...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Koton, koton, kotokotokoton...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I've always known my final destination...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...there, the top of the fifth hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see you there... at the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So... aren't you hungry yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can make apple juice! It's good for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...and it's quick and easy... if you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have eggs and milk, I can make custard pudding!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's cornstarch, I can make {\i1}manju{\i0} too. Mine's really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fix something. Please give me a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.14,0:05:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh also, I called Kaoru-no-Kimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She should be right over!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.25,0:05:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This won't turn on...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My Dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no fruit, and not even milk or butter...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...just a little bit of old frozen food...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.75,0:06:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All the windows closed,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.94,0:06:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...in this room filled with mirrors...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.71,0:06:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Returning each day from school to this dark, ice-cold room alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...with nothing here to eat... How on earth can she live?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear brother, I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:07:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I called you like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I didn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How's her fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.03,0:07:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Still very high.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.77,0:07:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A pretty high fever...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I like it that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.96,0:07:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a masochist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this! Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still wearing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back to me! Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.44,0:07:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why must you wear this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.03,0:08:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing is a curse you've placed on yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it ba...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the curse of Miya-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you wear this, you'll stay trapped under her curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to throw it into the bottom of the canal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Damned thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.05,0:09:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing will change!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing will change while you wear that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.27,0:09:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that, so why won't you take it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotokoton...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.19,0:09:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Koton, koton, kotokotokoton...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.07,0:09:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, take care of Saint-Juste?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, forget what you saw today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please pretend it was all a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That scar, hidden under the bracelet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.21,0:10:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...I tried to avoid imagining what could have caused it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But it kept coming back to me, that hidden scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.35,0:10:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help but think... Suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know her past...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But, knowing her now, it could be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a favor to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you go to the elm tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.63,0:11:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe... she is there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you still talking like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You had to wait in the rain, and caught this fever!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.84,0:11:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so obsessed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.45,0:11:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tolerate such a thing, myself, easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's different if it is {\i1}her{\i0} getting wet in the rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.86,0:11:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I could not tolerate such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go to the elm tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.84,0:11:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to lose my temper with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.39,0:11:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... I'm sorry. Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can be so difficult!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.94,0:11:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaving the cram-session right in the middle...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I was worrying about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.88,0:11:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Everyone's already gone home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.56,0:11:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,May I come by to pick up my bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:12:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave your bag to Shinobu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You can get it from her tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, then... the umbrella you loaned me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.21,0:12:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's okay....
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm truly sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll say goodbye—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Something must have happened to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.29,0:12:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...when you went to school to get your notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.96,0:12:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! No... nothing really! Not at school...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.43,0:12:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The rain, it was the rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.72,0:12:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So I got wet... and felt a bit ill... so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So... I rested at a friend's house...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko! Arikura Tomoko, she's in Section A—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.84,0:12:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If you felt ill, then that was the only thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.89,0:12:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.94,0:12:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Good-night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.56,0:13:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the curse of Miya-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you wear this, you'll stay trapped under her curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.01,0:13:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.36,0:13:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it early for you to be up already?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We're having a cram session at the Sorority House this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well! A sandwich?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. We'll have breakfast after the study session.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You never liked tomatoes before...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.73,0:14:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come to like them...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.09,0:14:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I need my vitamin A.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.56,0:14:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.85,0:14:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's her "vitamin A".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now now, don't get in the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sandwiches...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I seem to recall you making one for my lunch once...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... I think your mother had a cold that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It was really tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.39,0:14:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure... Next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.08,0:15:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Vitamin A?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.20,0:15:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.48,0:15:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no cram session. I lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Mom and Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.19,0:15:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Strangely enough, my dear brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...this is something which seems to deeply touch my heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...and even if I have to lie or disobey someone, I must act.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.94,0:15:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, she must eat some nutritious food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She must be still sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:16:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"How are you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"I decided to bring you a box-lunch."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,"Please eat a lot and sleep tight."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.43,0:16:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"Get healthy soon."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Very soon, please, very soon."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.45,0:16:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"I brought you a sandwich, a salad, and coffee..."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"Please feel better soon."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That should do. If she eats it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.39,0:16:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? Here's your bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.56,0:16:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It had started to rain furiously!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of time had passed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.55,0:17:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...and you still weren't back when the session ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When we called the school, the custodian said there was no one there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The thought of an accident happening to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...made us more and more worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mona-Lisa-sama and Borgia-sama had left...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.39,0:17:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama and I were the only ones left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I had to leave myself, shortly after ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.73,0:17:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I called her around 10:30 and apologized.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe not quite enough, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Was your apology accepted?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.89,0:17:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.02,0:17:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh good, I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.87,0:17:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Having Miya-sama upset at you can be very bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.71,0:17:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.30,0:17:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So what was it? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.52,0:17:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, I won't tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.82,0:17:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Later! I'll tell you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Nanako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! I've got to talk to Tomoko quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.44,0:17:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,An alibi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.71,0:17:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,An alibi? Yes... I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I happened to use you as an alibi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I told them that I was at your place...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.88,0:18:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if anyone asks, can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.25,0:18:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Asked by whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.39,0:18:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father and mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.31,0:18:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! You're in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no! It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... in short, it's for the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.92,0:18:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Sure, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.76,0:18:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially Miya-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.61,0:18:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it! Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks! I'll explain later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay. You just owe me one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.50,0:18:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the first session came and went.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:18:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the second.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.08,0:19:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The third session began and got to lunch time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.12,0:19:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I worried the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.18,0:19:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I resolved then to return the umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.96,0:19:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't like it, throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get too close to Asaka Rei-san
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.67,0:20:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't get close to her intentionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It just happened that I was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.98,0:20:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,With her, in the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.04,0:20:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems to have taken the day off...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Was she okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Afterwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She was fine. She fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What about her fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I had her take some aspirin right away...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...but it wasn't too effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She takes too many drugs already, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.61,0:21:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I meet you after school?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.17,0:21:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,To talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this regarding?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Under the elm tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The elm tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.46,0:21:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, under the elm tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.01,0:21:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Four forty eight and thirty seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.99,0:21:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Four forty eight and forty seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.07,0:21:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Four forty eight and fifty seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.08,0:22:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Four forty nine and zero seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.18,0:22:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It was no coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.57,0:22:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted Mariko-san and Tomoko to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.24,0:22:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That way I could visit Saint-Juste-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.20,0:22:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure why I wanted to...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.58,0:22:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I wanted to see that elm tree again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.47,0:22:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...the one Saint-Juste stood under for so long in the rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.69,0:22:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.12,0:23:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.06,0:23:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You know already.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.21,0:23:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.08,0:23:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the elm tree where Rei waited for you yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She got soaked and caught a fever!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.33,0:23:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you care at all what happens to Rei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.42,0:23:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't concern me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.85,0:23:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.47,0:23:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But Rei is your younger sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.01,0:24:14.21,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.21,0:24:19.68,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.15,0:24:25.29,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.29,0:24:30.76,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.50,0:24:37.04,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.04,0:24:42.51,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.51,0:24:45.24,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.24,0:24:48.05,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.05,0:24:50.45,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.45,0:24:55.72,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.83,0:25:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Feelings of doom, due to Miya-sama's curse,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.68,0:25:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...fill Saint-Juste with hopeless depression and cynicism.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.21,0:25:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako, worried about Saint-Juste,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.80,0:25:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...goes to the clock tower to look for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.43,0:25:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei embraces Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.24,0:25:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...and whispers something in her ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.62,0:25:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode: A Tale of Double Suicide
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.59,0:25:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, Dear Brother... There is no end to my tears...
